/target
# Cargo.lock is intentionally tracked for this workspace.
# The CI runs `cargo <cmd> --locked` which requires the lock file to be
# present in the repository.  Soroban dependency ranges are broad enough
# that an unlocked build can silently select incompatible transitive versions.

